{
  "stem": "3994.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when my middle sister, [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Mengele ?] inspected-- [? show ?] [INAUDIBLE] you are healthy and everything-- he told her to go one the other side.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When she went on the other side, and [?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Mengele ?] went away from us-- because first row and then he went further-- I told my sister, would you come back and I go there?",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that's how I saved my life.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He couldn't see me that I was pregnant.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[COUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my other sisters came to same place like me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were all healthy to go to work.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We went back to our barracks.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The next morning we were shifted on the train to work.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "How long had you been in Auschwitz for by this stage?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Beg your pardon?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Auschwitz?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think we were there two or three months.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I can't remember, really, how long I was there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Do you remember-- It was too long, anyhow.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I can't remember the date when we came from Hungary.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know if I gave it to you.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I can't remember on the right date.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Anyhow, when we went on the train and the train was moving, one of Polish girl who were there for a long time already and she notice that I am pregnant.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She wanted to pull me out of the train.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then I told her, I have something in my mouth.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "If she doesn't tell anybody or doesn't pull me off, I give it to her, but only when the train were moving and I went.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that was very naive, because she could have stopped the train or anything to do.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I had a diamond in my mouth.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I gave it to her.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I had it in the back in my mouth.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
